sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI as RAGCommand
    participant SVC as RAGService
    participant VR as VectorRepository
    participant GW as ZoteroGateway

    CLI->>SVC: query(prompt, top_k)
    SVC->>SVC: embed_text(prompt)
    SVC->>VR: search(embedding, top_k)
    VR-->>SVC: List[SearchResult] (item_keys only)
    
    Note over SVC, GW: Sullivan Protocol: Hydration Phase
    loop for each result
        SVC->>GW: get_item(item_key)
        GW-->>SVC: ZoteroItem
        SVC->>SVC: attach item to SearchResult
    end

    SVC-->>CLI: List[SearchResult] (with Metadata)
    CLI->>CLI: Render Rich Table / JSON
